      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHASING KISSES (5) broke her maiden last start by 3 lengths at Richmond Straight over 324m (17.80). Looks the one to beat. HANDS ON TINA (3) goes very well this course and distance starting six times for two wins and two minors. Placed last time (22.38) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 2.5 lengths. Can feature in the finish. BIGBAD EDEN (1) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Maiden at this track. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the rails draw. Expected to bounce back to best. JEANNA (2) has been freshened for this and can hit the frame.",
